description.tr: Tatsumaki, en büyük botlardan biri olmakla birlikte içinde kullanıcı profilleri, seviyeler ve basit moderasyon sistemi bulunmakta.
description.en: Tatsumaki is providing social aspects including member profiles, levels, fun stuff & simple moderation.
description.ga_IE: Tá TAtsumaki ag soláthar gnéithe sóisialta lena n-áirítear próifílí ball, leibhéil, stuif spraoi agus modhnóireacht shimplí.
